  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Pink Phone Revolution Cambodia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will bring at least 80 direct beneficiaries in 5provinces, enabling women&apos;s groups to get access to and share information. We&apos;ll work closely with the livelihood team, Ministry of Women Affair and the NGO partner  - Women for Prosperity to gather information to distribute to selected women&apos;s group via SMS. Also, keep track of all message sent and received to monitor effectiveness and at same time working with beneficiaries on the mobile training to build capacity. This project will create awareness of the Pink Phone scheme with local telecoms service, technical partners and government to reach the targeted aims.</narrative>
  </description>
